data.description: This quaint cottage type home is located in the heart of Cortez.  The large kitchen is one of the great features.  It has many custom cabinets and a large pantry with a lot of storage.  The hardwood floors have been newly restored and are beautiful.  It has 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  The home has a great open floor plan.  There is truly a custom feel with the many built in storage and closets.  I love the glass door knobs.  There is a large utility room.  There is an oversized 3 car garage with many shelving units.  The property has a large 3 room storage on the property that has storage and a workshop.  The property is beautifully landscaped with flowers and roses and your very own apple tree.  CALL FOR A SHOWING TODAY.
